### 🧪 Error Handling HTTP Test Client

# Konfigurasi Environment
@hostname = localhost
@port = 5000
@host = http://{{hostname}}:{{port}}

###
# 1. Test Endpoint Normal (200 OK)
GET {{host}}/api/demo/ok

###

# 2. Test Bad Request (400 Bad Request)
GET {{host}}/api/demo/bad-request

###

# 3. Test Not Found (404 Not Found)
GET {{host}}/api/demo/not-found

###

# 4. Test Conflict (409 Conflict)
GET {{host}}/api/demo/conflict

###

# 5. Test Server Error (500 Internal Server Error)
GET {{host}}/api/demo/server-error
